OL,3,CFamilies welcome the Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdecision to scrap the two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,FRachel Reeves said her measures were
OL,8,Fthe right choice for a fairer,
OL,9,Fstronger and more secure Britain,
OL,10,Fadding that they would provide
OL,11,F"immediate relief for families".
OL,13,FAt the Bounce and Rhyme group in
OL,14,FNewton Abbott, ITV West Country spoke
OL,15,Fto Jonathan & Anna who have three
OL,16,Fchildren, including 11-month-old twins
OL,17,FTess and Cara about the removal of the
OL,18,Ftwo-child benefit cap.
