OL,3,CFamilies welcome the Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdecision to scrap the two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,FJonathan said: "There are millions of
OL,8,Fchildren in this country in poverty
OL,9,Fand it was a Victorian, disgusting
OL,10,Fpolicy so it's brilliant that that's
OL,11,Fbeen removed.
OL,13,F"We have a demographic shift in this
OL,14,Fcountry so it's important to remove
OL,15,Fbarriers to people raising families.
OL,16,FIt's the biggest single thing they
OL,17,Fcould have done to move children out
OL,18,Fof poverty."
