OL,3,CFamilies welcome the Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdecision to scrap the two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,FAnna added: "What's a Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment for if they can't make
OL,9,Fchanges like that?"
OL,11,FAlso at the group, Shanay, with 8-
OL,12,Fmonth-old Sully, said: "Everything has
OL,13,Fgone up in price, it's difficult to
OL,14,Fmanage but doable."
OL,16,FIn other moves in the budget, the 5p
OL,17,Fcut in fuel duty is being maintained
OL,18,Funtil September 2026. Meanwhile,
OL,19,Fexisting freezes to personal tax
OL,20,Fthresholds are being extended for
OL,21,Fanother three years until 2030-31.
